title: The Art Institute of Chicago Dual-Color Pencil Set
description:
This set of 6 of dual-color pencils featuring a different color at each end: pink, blue, brown, yellow, green, red, orange, purple, black and white. A compact option for creative people.

  • 6 pencils.
  • Pencil dimension: 7 in.
  • 12 different color leads.
  • Plastic Art Institute of Chicago slipcover.
